            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>WebP offers the best quality-to-file-size ratio for most use cases. Google recommends it, all modern browsers support it, and it's typically 25-35% smaller than JPEG at comparable quality. AVIF is even smaller where browser support suits your audience.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
